{"tid":1308128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小明的精神","createTime":"2019-07-11T21:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:52:26.000Z","uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c00eafa3ef53f98e44f46a9d9490eec7d2d2a12","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:18:14.000Z","msg":"小明很憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n他看見小光在打小峰，班主任卻視而不見。<br />\n<br />\n不止小明看見了，班上眾多的同學也看見了，大家也心有不憤。<br />\n<br />\n為了令更多人知道這不合理的暴行，小明和眾多志同道合的同學在學校宣傳壁報版上貼了很多關於此事的證據，以及支持小峰的話。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道了，連隔壁學校的校長也開聲發話要求徹查。<br />\n<br />\n學校依然視而不見。<br />\n<br />\n小明更加憤怒了。<br />\n<br />\n所以當他在看到小光的好友小方在撕毀壁報時，他忍不住上去和他理論。<br />\n<br />\n但他同時記著老師的教誨，不能以暴易暴。<br />\n<br />\n結果小方不由分說地打在他面上，還嘲笑他一番。<br />\n<br />\n小明流血了。<br />\n<br />\n其他看到的人也憤怒了，扶著小明起來的同時不斷指罵小方。<br />\n<br />\n小方也不敢回應眾人的唾罵，跑回了小光身邊。<br />\n<br />\n小明笑了，因為大家終於覺醒了，小光作惡的盡頭到了。<br />\n<br />\n一切都是值得的，我要作一個好榜樣，給大家看到小光的惡。<br />\n<br />\n只是鼻子很痛就是了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「他舉起右手，用力的在自己臉上臉打了兩個嘴吧，熱辣辣的有些痛；打完之後，便心平氣和起來，似乎打的是自己，被打的識別一個自己，不久也就彷彿是自己打了別個一般，──雖然還有些熱辣辣，──心滿意足的得勝躺了下來。」<br />\n                                   ──魯迅 &lt;&lt;呀Q正傳&gt;&gt;"},{"pid":"3e257b212bb7f65e0ae9953def78a3eed4d49f5e","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:23:03.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"d0894144b37056ab25bb6660972887f41b8e92ec","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4113830d132c9480dbafc84ad4b17f8d5eacf40","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:25:29.000Z","msg":"止戈為武"},{"pid":"6c408a165cc16707b1d8ff72d4fede66ff714b79","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:27:52.000Z","msg":"以德報怨，以何報德？<br />\n<br />\n以德報德，以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直</span>報怨"},{"pid":"bdef2af1257036a387e90c28543e99d459ef50c4","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:31:47.000Z","msg":"一名男子凌晨在淘大花園對開的「連儂牆」前，被另一名男子連番拳打臉部，沒有避開或擋駕，他一度倒地，由其他人扶起，涉事男子其後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n人權監察副主席、本身是律師的莊耀洸表示，被打的人雖然可能會感動到其他人，但被拳打頭部，有機會造成身體嚴重傷害，當事人應該立即離開或者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">自衛</span></span>；在這種情況下的自衛屬於<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">合法抗辯</span></span>，自衛後亦要與對方保持距離，以免加劇情況。<br />\n<br />\n莊耀洸又認為，在目前社會狀況下，市民需要保持克制，避免動武，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在場人士亦應該制止</span></span>。今次事件，有目擊者攝錄過程，可以成為證據之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467788-20190711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467788-20190711.htm&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0M22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=0211e6a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467788-20190711.htm&h=be8d5206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467788-20190711.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ad5df6e8ee1c35fa2c72eb9737d218e44be5831e","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94556e0d5a5c92f39415601983884f16e3377ee7","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd494ea22c911d547951dd7d59a2d5ed0b53ad7b","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32872d72f6ab51d2de4023db73154339dcc6f787","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"唉。"},{"pid":"4fd8a86fdb1486268fc76c29af162090f3e928e1","tid":1308128,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"點解呢？"}]}